---
title: Tuscan Seitan Bolognese with Tagliatelle, Parmesan, and Chilies
description: Seitan, a wheat-based Japanese protein, lends heartiness to this vegetarian Bolognese. A touch of chili flakes gives this homemade tomato sauce an extra kick. Finished with nutty Parmesan, this is winter comfort food at its finest.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5658da43fd2cb95c7a8b4567.jpg
